<Link id="l00026" /><CodeLine lineNumber="26"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// This class is a wrapper to associative container MapT&lt;KeyT, ValueT&gt; using</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00027" /><CodeLine lineNumber="27"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// the hash value of the original key as the new key. This greatly improves the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00028" /><CodeLine lineNumber="28"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// performance of insert and query operations especially when hash values of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00029" /><CodeLine lineNumber="29"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// keys are available a priori, and reduces memory usage if KeyT has a large</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00030" /><CodeLine lineNumber="30"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// size.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00031" /><CodeLine lineNumber="31"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// All keys with the same hash value are considered equivalent (i.e. hash</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00032" /><CodeLine lineNumber="32"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// collision is silently ignored). Given such feature this class should only be</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00033" /><CodeLine lineNumber="33"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// used where it does not affect compilation correctness, for example, when</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00034" /><CodeLine lineNumber="34"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// loading a sample profile. The original key is not stored, so if the user</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00035" /><CodeLine lineNumber="35"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// needs to preserve it, it should be stored in the mapped type.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00036" /><CodeLine lineNumber="36"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Assuming the hashing algorithm is uniform, we use the formula</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00037" /><CodeLine lineNumber="37"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// 1 - Permute(n, k) / n ^ k where n is the universe size and k is number of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00038" /><CodeLine lineNumber="38"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// elements chosen at random to calculate the probability of collision. With</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00039" /><CodeLine lineNumber="39"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// 1,000,000 entries the probability is negligible:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00040" /><CodeLine lineNumber="40"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// 1 - (2^64)!/((2^64-1000000)!&#42;(2^64)^1000000) ~= 3&#42;10^-8.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00041" /><CodeLine lineNumber="41"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Source: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Birthday&#95;problem</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00042" /><CodeLine lineNumber="42"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00043" /><CodeLine lineNumber="43"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// \\param MapT The underlying associative container type.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00044" /><CodeLine lineNumber="44"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// \\param KeyT The original key type, which requires the implementation of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00045" /><CodeLine lineNumber="45"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   llvm::hash&#95;value(KeyT).</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00046" /><CodeLine lineNumber="46"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// \\param ValueT The original mapped type, which has the same requirement as</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00047" /><CodeLine lineNumber="47"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   the underlying container.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00048" /><CodeLine lineNumber="48"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// \\param MapTArgs Additional template parameters passed to the underlying</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00049" /><CodeLine lineNumber="49"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   container.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00050" /><CodeLine lineNumber="50"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">template</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &lt;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">template</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &lt;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">typename</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">typename</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">typename</span><span class="doxyHighlight">...&gt; </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">typename</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> MapT,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00051" /><CodeLine lineNumber="51"><span class="doxyHighlight">          </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">typename</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> KeyT, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">typename</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> ValueT, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">typename</span><span class="doxyHighlight">... MapTArgs&gt;</span></CodeLine>
